articles.title: Getting second Covid-19 infection not more dangerous, say S'pore experts rebutting US study - The Straits Times
articles.description:
The American study had suggested that those infected with Covid-19 a second time are at higher risk of organ failure and death.
 Read more at straitstimes.com.
